{"timestamp": "2025-12-05 20:26:59.943531", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission recorded.\n\nSummary of submission:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- faulty_devices: host_1_1_1_1, host_1_3_1_1\n- root_cause_name: host_missing_ip\n\nRecommended next steps (brief):\n- Verify DHCP leases on DHCP server and check logs for the affected hosts' MACs.\n- Check DHCP client status / system logs on the affected hosts and restart DHCP client if needed.\n- Query ip addr / ip route on additional hosts flagged \"unknown\" to assess scope.\n- If many hosts are affected, investigate DHCP service health (dhcp_service_down) and network-level DHCP relay/path issues.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2695, "output_tokens": 137, "total_tokens": 2832, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1664}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
